#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:2
msgid "代码审计"
msgstr "Code Audit"

#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:5
msgid "简介"
msgstr "Overview"

#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:6
msgid "代码审计是找到应用缺陷的过程。其通常有白盒审计、黑盒审计、灰盒审计等方式。白盒审计指通过对源代码的分析找到应用缺陷，黑盒审计通常不涉及到源代码，多使用模糊测试的方式，而灰盒审计则是黑白结合的方式。三种不同的测试方法有不同的优缺点。"
msgstr "Code audit is the process of finding defects in an application. Common approaches include white-box auditing, black-box auditing, and gray-box auditing. White-box auditing finds application defects by analyzing source code. Black-box auditing usually does not involve source code and often relies on fuzzing. Gray-box auditing combines both approaches. These three testing methods have different advantages and disadvantages."

#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:9
msgid "常用概念"
msgstr "Common Concepts"

#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:12
msgid "输入"
msgstr "Input"

#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:13
msgid "输入通常也称Source，Web应用的输入可以是请求的参数（GET、POST等）、上传的文件、Cookie、数据库数据等用户可控或者间接可控的地方。"
msgstr "Input is also commonly called a Source. In a web application, input can come from request parameters such as GET and POST, uploaded files, Cookies, database data, and other locations that are directly or indirectly controllable by users."

#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:15
msgid ""
"例如PHP中的 ``$_GET`` / ``$_POST`` / ``$_REQUEST`` / ``$_COOKIE`` / "
"``$_FILES``  / ``$_SERVER`` 等，都可以作为应用的输入。"
msgstr ""
"For example, in PHP, ``$_GET`` / ``$_POST`` / ``$_REQUEST`` / ``$_COOKIE`` "
"/ ``$_FILES``  / ``$_SERVER`` can all be treated as application input."

#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:18
msgid "处理函数"
msgstr "Handler Functions"

#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:19
msgid "处理函数是对数据进行过滤或者编解码的函数，通常被称为Clean/Filter/Sanitizer。这些函数会对输入进行安全操作或过滤，为漏洞利用带来不确定性。"
msgstr "Handler functions are functions that filter, encode, or decode data. They are often called Clean, Filter, or Sanitizer functions. These functions perform security processing or filtering on input, which introduces uncertainty into exploitability."

#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:21
msgid ""
"同样以PHP为例，这样的函数可能是 ``mysqli_real_escape_string`` / ``htmlspecialchars`` / "
"``base64_encode`` / ``str_rot13`` 等，也可能是应用自定义的过滤函数。"
msgstr ""
"Using PHP again as an example, such functions may include "
"``mysqli_real_escape_string`` / ``htmlspecialchars`` / ``base64_encode`` / "
"``str_rot13``, or application-defined filtering functions."

#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:24
msgid "危险函数"
msgstr "Dangerous Functions"

#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:25
msgid "危险函数又常叫做Sink Call、漏洞点，是可能触发危险行为如文件操作、命令执行、数据库操作等行为的函数。"
msgstr "Dangerous functions are also commonly called Sink Calls or vulnerability points. They are functions that may trigger dangerous behavior such as file operations, command execution, or database operations."

#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:27
msgid "在PHP中，可能是 ``include`` / ``system`` / ``echo`` 等。"
msgstr "In PHP, examples may include ``include`` / ``system`` / ``echo``."

#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:30
msgid "自动化审计"
msgstr "Automated Auditing"

#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:31
msgid ""
"一般认为一个漏洞的触发过程是从输入经过过滤到危险函数的过程(Source To "
"Sink)，而审计就是寻找这个链条的过程。常见的自动化审计方案有危险函数匹配、控制流分析等。"
msgstr ""
"A vulnerability is generally considered to be triggered when data flows from"
" input through filtering to a dangerous function, a Source To Sink path. "
"Auditing is the process of finding this chain. Common automated audit "
"approaches include dangerous function matching and control flow analysis."

#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:34
msgid "危险函数匹配"
msgstr "Dangerous Function Matching"

#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:35
msgid "白盒审计最常见的方式是通过搜寻危险函数与危险参数定位漏洞，比较有代表性的工具是Seay开发的审计工具。这种方法误报率相当高，这是因为这种方法没有对程序的流程进行深入分析，另一方面，这种方式通常是孤立地分析每一个文件，忽略了文件之间复杂的调用关系。"
msgstr "The most common white-box auditing method locates vulnerabilities by searching for dangerous functions and dangerous parameters. A representative example is the audit tool developed by Seay. This method has a relatively high false-positive rate because it does not deeply analyze program flow. It also usually analyzes each file in isolation and ignores complex call relationships between files."

#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:37
msgid "具体的说，这种方式在一些环境下能做到几乎无漏报，只要审计者有耐心，可以发现大部分的漏洞，但是在高度框架化的代码中，能找到的漏洞相对有限。"
msgstr "More specifically, in some environments this approach can achieve almost no false negatives. If the auditor is patient, most vulnerabilities can be found. However, in highly framework-driven code, the number of vulnerabilities it can find is relatively limited."

#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:40
msgid "控制流分析"
msgstr "Control Flow Analysis"

#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:41
msgid "在后来的系统中，考虑到一定程度引入AST作为分析的依据，在一定程度上减少了误报，但是仍存在很多缺陷。"
msgstr "Later systems introduced ASTs as an analysis basis to some extent, which reduced false positives, but many limitations remained."

#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:43
msgid ""
"而后，Dahse  "
"J等人设计了RIPS，该工具进行数据流与控制流分析，结合过程内与过程间的分析得到审计结果，相对危险函数匹配的方式来说误报率少了很多，但是同样的也增加了开销。"
msgstr ""
"Later, Dahse J et al. designed RIPS, which performs data flow and control "
"flow analysis and combines intraprocedural and interprocedural analysis to "
"produce audit results. Compared with dangerous function matching, it has "
"many fewer false positives, but it also increases cost."

#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:46
msgid "基于图的分析"
msgstr "Graph-Based Analysis"

#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:47
msgid ""
"基于图的分析是对控制流分析的一个改进，其利用CFG的特性和图计算的算法，一定程度上简化了计算，比较有代表性的是微软的Semmle QL和NDSS "
"2017年发表的文章Efficient and Flexible Discovery of PHP Application "
"Vulnerabilities。"
msgstr ""
"Graph-based analysis is an improvement over control flow analysis. It uses "
"CFG properties and graph-computation algorithms to simplify computation to "
"some extent. Representative examples include Microsoft's Semmle QL and the "
"NDSS 2017 paper Efficient and Flexible Discovery of PHP Application "
"Vulnerabilities."

#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:50
msgid "代码相似性比对"
msgstr "Code Similarity Comparison"

#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:51
msgid "一些开发者会复制其他框架的代码，或者使用各种框架。如果事先有建立对应的漏洞图谱，则可使用相似性方法来找到漏洞。"
msgstr "Some developers copy code from other frameworks or use various frameworks. If a corresponding vulnerability map has been built in advance, similarity methods can be used to find vulnerabilities."

#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:54
msgid "灰盒分析"
msgstr "Gray-Box Analysis"

#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:55
msgid "基于控制流的分析开销较大，于是有人提出了基于运行时的分析方式，对代码进行Hook，当执行到危险函数时自动回溯输入，找到输入并判断是否可用。"
msgstr "Control-flow-based analysis is expensive, so runtime-based analysis has been proposed. This approach hooks the code and, when execution reaches a dangerous function, automatically traces back to the input, identifies the input, and determines whether it is usable."

#: ../../source/misc/audit.rst:57
msgid "这种方式解决了控制流分析实现复杂、计算路径开销大的问题，在判断过滤函数上也有一定的突破，但是灰盒的方式并不一定会触发所有的漏洞。fate0开发的prvd就是基于这种设计思路。"
msgstr "This approach addresses the implementation complexity and high path-computation cost of control flow analysis, and it also improves handling of filtering functions. However, a gray-box approach does not necessarily trigger every vulnerability. prvd, developed by fate0, is based on this design."

